{"type": "article", "id": 60638, "title": "《啥是佩奇》导演的新作品依然不错，天猫开“好运理容店” | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人的一切", "date": "2019-01-25T04:34:44Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 12153, "name": "Riccardo Tisci"}, {"id": 189, "name": "Burberry"}, {"id": 48458, "name": "老板电器"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 1480589, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 45, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190125114407Qzyg2783olCXZvwR.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p line=\"fO0K\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4331956608787207?\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>王一博成为植村秀全球品牌大使，</b></a>并且上妆示范植村秀的大盘眼影。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201901251144436nKAvqpmIkLsEuOe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190125114444179O0vHQiMSRLDZN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>值得一看的 Case</h3><p line=\"9DBA\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MTg3MDk4MQ==&amp;mid=2653147592&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=446aba6674596a6d0196858e0d1323ee&amp;chksm=bd7988a28a0e01b4ed0a6a28e4dc592de9a00da5f2544c724e7b74843f22694b79a3173ffd3d&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=0125zLyFqzFkNPmMUjXVUdbI&amp;key=a75ab368dd20a79899ff271f04b4d99abd76cca2ec8af54d1b2885c3570b4863faf391df37a04bdfc5e7fb4127eba9555a40813bd003f69e8618f413f41ad6c5d90fb91274b874ccf909121b2bc57241&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14+build(18A391)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=ID3wLkrNihH0UC3l7cxT6W28IOLZb93zlk6Gl8ICVhDfcd%2BYAG3e9qsuNG%2FYxYci\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>老板电器的新春广告把视角放在婆婆和妈妈身上。</b></a>片中双方准备去年的年夜饭时，由于双方不同的烹饪理念和不够称心的厨房电器，矛盾不少。继而铺陈今年换了电器，问题也解决了。</p><p line=\"BdJZ\">这个广告片是《啥是佩奇》导演张大鹏的新作品，创意代理商来自 karma。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=v083170od67\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"16Bz\"><b><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MzYxMjI0NQ==&amp;mid=2659129968&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=4388d25ed63fbf39bf56dda2e584a38e&amp;chksm=bd1fd2ca8a685bdc6ceb2ba99605f73a21e94f04219d8901ca0c066b5c0e61fb927c8454ad8c&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=0125wmLGgJZBAJSvs68JL6dy&amp;key=22211bbfbb5c89f7455e45d1543e7bda49327b336aa419445f22abb98539de1c3668b5c89b974ea21ed0917d8b9946325fb940f1f41d04d429ea62d953dd86f76a68a64e6143ee92d9210dbbad831412&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14+build(18A391)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=ID3wLkrNihH0UC3l7cxT6W28IOLZb93zlk6Gl8ICVhDfcd%2BYAG3e9qsuNG%2FYxYci\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">肯德基和电影《疯狂的外星人》联合推出广告片“疯狂是开始的力量” </a>，</b>片中宁浩和黄渤回忆两个人合作的过往。黄渤既是肯德基新春形象代言人，也是宁浩导演的“疯狂”电影的主演。电影将在春节期间上映，广告片自然是双方的联合营销活动。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=v00293eexf2\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"FiIQ\"><a href=\"https://fx.weico.net/share/54681756.html?weibo_id=4332023554500852\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>天猫和贝克汉姆创立的男士理容品牌 HOUSE99 开设了间“好运理容店”。</b></a>店内设计成复古风格，在旧式玻璃柜台内摆放商品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190125114557HGeRZcMIDiPB7A1V.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190125114559tvdfKl0XBWOD7Vc6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190125114614qz0A5KQh86xkYEfX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666255\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190125114557wE8cgBIC2W5F1uGs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190125114558Q06lNheTJ2wD8Ru3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201901251146492f8XotyHrzk5YZmx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"x0WW\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5NDgwNjgxMw==&amp;mid=2651752518&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=f1cc26036403b934ae72da71069acb25&amp;chksm=bd7805348a0f8c2219e97ccc8246302a707ce90032ef415f26fb389e474415a45112814e9100&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=01248S0Lsl9erVZ2H7binsLt&amp;key=f1dfc5c7113b93466aedf57b7916be16adb6a0b37036819c3e531679b7e60fb4f8195c2d74eebab46b78dcbecc54c97b35a76c41cc4fd561a5f4ddfdfd3fa0785dcb3fb28a3da59b30db54b35a477d1e&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14+build(18A391)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=ID3wLkrNihH0UC3l7cxT6W28IOLZb93zlk6Gl8ICVhDfcd%2BYAG3e9qsuNG%2FYxYci\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Riccardo Tisci 担任 Burberry 创意总监后的首支广告片发布，</b></a>诠释 “Kingdom 王者之都”的主题，共找来 6 位不同风格的摄影师来拍摄 Burberry 的 2019 春夏系列。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190125114753b2zV9WcO0ZoC354H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190125114753J0Es2eGwlpj59KN1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190125114753fAPsNd1QE6Viw2oY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190125114754HvMom84CO2dnWr0w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190125114754mnEybiwULo7B92CN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190125114754G9lIU7hBFWdaOTHS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190125114755mfPKUC2BsjN7eVan.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"Zla1\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MTg1MjM1NTk2MA==&amp;mid=2348035556&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=0cdc617b4928e4ea7647b04a4533b2cc&amp;chksm=4857cff37f2046e5a0dfd22125b9423bfb7da44aee32133b32d6978e94f3005e85b9b0559bec&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=0124kWWKSvGQ7PTQ4W2P9gGE&amp;key=8fc76d7ce7187a055b077125afc22fb9c47e1e32711ac64c42291137295c935911ae883cc65b577b6cada5a8cd4b504949485a2e75d3a2beaccd07d496c50f5c37cabeef33b5ce2b23091b6d983d63a8&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14+build(18A391)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=ID3wLkrNihH0UC3l7cxT6W28IOLZb93zlk6Gl8ICVhDfcd%2BYAG3e9qsuNG%2FYxYci\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Nike 新年广告主题是“齐上阵 亮新招” ，</b></a>发布“新春贺岁”系列服饰和鞋款，传递穿新衣展现潮流个性的理念。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=s08316wjlpy\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"0s6Z\"><b>YSL 推广新品细管口红，找来演员<a href=\"https://fx.weico.net/share/54680309.html?weibo_id=4332047449682869\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">辛芷蕾</a>和歌手<a href=\"https://fx.weico.net/share/54680252.html?weibo_id=4332062368558016\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">马伯骞</a>演绎不同的口红色号。</b>片中把红外线和吸管口红管的外形对应了起来。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=k0831uh20sm\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=p0831ldt194\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"EbjF\"><strong>美汁源推出 8 种不同的新年定制化瓶身，</strong>包括多金、腹肌、好运、陪伴、顺利、脱单、有房和涨薪。 消费者通过支付宝 AR 扫描可以获得现金红包、饿了么优惠券等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190125114903j0MLO8YrkwFSzifT.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707692\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190125114902MQ76myxiuPGVRfkC.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.660900\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190125114902Fyvsxikt0XPR3zBm.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.774026\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"V2Qp\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v68ANY62PC0&amp;feature=youtu.be\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>汉堡王和 DoorDash 发布了超级碗的先导片，这是它 13 年后再次回到超级碗。</b></a>片中国王精心准备和憧憬即将到来的活动，包括检查麦克风和把桌子擦更干净。结尾提示观看者可以获得 DoorDash 的神秘礼盒。此外，正片中汉堡王的重点依然是皇堡。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=c0831alufh4\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"KHa0\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZcwiS8w70T8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Expensify 超级碗广告找来说唱明星 2 Chainz 和高尔夫球冠军 Adam Scott 出演。</b></a></p><p line=\"KHa0\">Expensify 是款扫描收据并储存图像的应用，片中 Adam Scott  担任唱片公司的财务负责人，2 Chainz 在无趣的费用对谈中入睡，然后用说唱的形式吐槽财务管理的方式。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=y0831gmfw1x\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"KHa0\" class=\"\">题图来自：<a href=\"https://unsplash.com/photos/CSWcbb_FriU?utm_source=unsplash&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_content=creditCopyText\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">PNG Design</a> on <a href=\"https://unsplash.com/search/photos/burberry?utm_source=unsplash&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_content=creditCopyText\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Unsplash</a></p>"}